{"tid":667184,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［疑難雜症］開冷氣時車頭有雜音","createTime":"2018-05-16T13:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T15:45:22.000Z","uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbff7dcdfd61a932282bcbdc92868a9714fc6cc","tid":667184,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"今朝早上都一切正常，到六點幾收工開車就出事。<br />\n<br />\n著車開冷氣，車頭左邊有傳出明顯的「噠噠噠噠」聲，聲音大小隨冷氣大小增減，但奇怪的是冷氣係凍的。<br />\n<br />\n想問問各巴打以下屬咩情況多？<br />\n現在情況除了搵車房外有什麼可以做？<br />\n最壞打算換冷氣泵的話，係咪需要去搵定料或者一般包料連人工幾錢到？<br />\n<br />\n（想問左等自己心底有數，以免日後去車房被劏）<br />\n<br />\n車：06年 Benz SLK200<br />\n<br />\n求各高手巴打指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a2a8a0302c894e3b6ad95902751edee586427c","tid":667184,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"會唔會只係皮帶響"},{"pid":"fb36304884ea5532a32da43078b31644547f74b2","tid":667184,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"似係吹風機摩打撻左牙，好少野但好似要起錶台整"},{"pid":"e5004963660d374f463a66518447677091d5aaa5","tid":667184,"uid":96400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"2006 slk病痛應該一浪接一浪<br />\n早日換車<br />\n<br />\n車頭嘈係高年份Benz 特徵<br />\n小問題的話，你整一整我估3000-5000"},{"pid":"fbca9432e99f80f5594b7ef38a07c1b3848af6b6","tid":667184,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"俾個keyword 你問：淇誠<br />\n整開benz<br />\n利申客仔"},{"pid":"a9ae7b1f4af456c82fd26bcf1f1a530f0237a124","tid":667184,"uid":8975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"我之前架IS200都係咁<br />\n不過冇野冇問題又渣得我廢事整<br />\n渣多左半年就賣左車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}